It's a spice client for openstack instance (spice supported), based on virt-verwer

virt-viewer address https://github.com/SPICE/virt-viewer

There are just three files modified and two added.


Modified files: 

remote-viewer.h  added some method declaration

remote-viewer.c  implemented method added in remote-viewer.h

and changed the native connect_dialog method

Makefile   added "-lcurl -ljansson"


Added files:

openstack.ini for configuring controller node ip

back.jpg  background picture in login dialog
